{"tid":55894,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港真係好多仆街廢老","createTime":"2016-12-26T17:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T19:01:37.000Z","uid":29134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6439ed167ca89c171765d34112269b647e1ca469","tid":55894,"uid":29134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:57:47.000Z","msg":"咁小弟整親隻腳<br />\n呢幾日都係紮住隻腳<br />\n今日同女朋友搭西鐵去搵朋友<br />\n一上車見到兩個關愛座無人坐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻腳紮成咁我仲唔可以坐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你坐啦我唔想比人批鬥<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我洗唔洗舉高隻腳比睇我整親（我真係舉左一下）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪咁撚on9啦<br />\n如是者一個企一個坐過左一分鐘<br />\n有個呀伯跑左過黎坐低<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （細細聲）唉，明明老人位，後生仔都坐既<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我整親隻腳呀呀伯（拎起隻腳比佢睇）<br />\n咁呀伯就無聲出<br />\n咁見佢頭先咁大枝野又細細聲到我岩岩聽到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉我怕撚左你啦整親腳都唔夠膽坐啦<br />\n比撚哂你坐啦<br />\n<br />\n之後就拖左女朋友行埋一邊企<br />\n關愛座唔係老人座<br />\n呀伯我已經忍左口無再屌你老母<br />\n你跑得咁撚快去個位仲要坐關愛座？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0cf21cf2c79299e858e7ea8895db9149ab22fd4","tid":55894,"uid":26749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T18:00:35.000Z","msg":"啱啱望住班蝗坐就無事<br />\n香港人坐就比啲廢老小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410bb96e33a602438cc2e2736a773e2f4e8c62c3","tid":55894,"uid":62754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T18:28:58.000Z","msg":"佢地好撚中意尖隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 你一話佢佢就會講：讓下老人家啦後生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次搭巴士 成人十幾蚊 長者淨係要個幾 仲要尖哂隊 連司機都忍唔住屌佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a988b7dc930176ad6fbd5fced23670e0a56d7b8d","tid":55894,"uid":17075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T19:01:07.000Z","msg":"上次等緊巴士 條隊入面有個廢老<br />\n之後架巴士一埋站就壞車 咁原本車上嘅乘客落車等第二架啦 <br />\n個死廢老居然趁個司機唔為意行去原本車上個埋乘客度 諗著陣間上車唔駛俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心d阿伯$2就咪呃啦仆佢地個臭街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e92bcd41f1ed390d576dd0775a99cfb71cc616c","tid":55894,"uid":17075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T19:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次等緊巴士 條隊入面有個廢老<br />\n之後架巴士一埋站就壞車 咁原本車上嘅乘客落車等第二架啦 <br />\n個死廢老居然趁個司機唔為意行去原本車上個<span style=\"color: red;\">堆</span>乘客度 諗著陣間上車唔駛俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心d阿伯$2就咪呃啦仆佢地個臭街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}